<div class="modal fade" id="report" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-md">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span><span class="sr-only">Close</span>
        </button>
        <h1 class="modal-title">回報問題</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="partA">
          非常非常感謝你/妳提供意見！ :D :D :D 願意的話，也請告訴我們怎麼聯絡你/妳吧 :)
        </div>
        <div class="partB">
          <form class="form-horizontal" id="reportform" method="post" action="/report">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="control-label col-sm-4">如何稱呼: </label>
              <div class="col-sm-8">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="name" placeholder="姓名或綽號 你方便稱呼的方式">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="control-label col-sm-4">聯絡方式: </label>
              <div class="col-sm-8">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="contact" placeholder="臉書或Email都可以喔">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="control-label col-sm-4">想說的話: </label>
              <div class="col-sm-8">
                <textarea rows="4" cols="50" name="comment" form="reportform" class="form-control"></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <div class="col-sm-offset-4 col-sm-8">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">送出</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
